{"tid":2186217,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–俄國神經毒素Novichok","createTime":"2020-09-02T20:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T21:18:04.000Z","uid":38861,"like":111,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"eac17d307753dcf8f710e89f7546137f91cafdd3","tid":2186217,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T20:50:17.000Z","msg":"2018年3月，前俄羅斯間謀Sergei Skripai及其女兒在英國被人下毒，毒藥被證實為蘇聯在冷戰時期所研發的神經毒素Novichok。<br />\n<br />\n2020年8月20日，一名極力反對普京的社會領袖Alexei Navalny，亦遭受到同類型的毒素傷害，表面證據暫時相信為被人在茶裡下毒。<br />\n<br />\n本篇深入淺出，將會簡述神經系統的運作，以及神經毒素Novichok的機制。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4VeNnwS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4VeNnwS.jpg&h=fa21d0d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖1）神經線負責傳遞信息，為身體內的橋樑。橋樑並不是緊密相扣著的，一條神經線質另一條神經線互相均有著一道空隙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YRyN6YE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYRyN6YE.jpg&h=52894268&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）訊息在神經線中主要是以電流的方式傳遞。<br />\n<br />\n電流來到神經線A的末端後，便會觸發ACh釋出，使ACh來到神經線之間的空隙。<br />\n<br />\nACh與另一神經線的Receptor結合後，便會觸發新一道的電流產生，使訊息一直能傳遞到終點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0wmsnw3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0wmsnw3.jpg&h=b87c1de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）神經線空隙的AChE負責分解ACh，以免電流長期持續產生。<br />\n<br />\n而俄國最愛的神經毒素Novichok則會與AChE合併及抑制AChE的功能，導致ACh不會被分解，使ACh無了期與神經線的Receptor結合，長期產生神經線電流的傳播，導致患者出現抽搐、癲癇等症狀，沒能適時治療的話更會導致死亡。<br />\n<br />\n解毒劑暫時有幾種，Atropine能阻截ACh與Receptor合併，Pralidoxime能夠促使Novichok無法與AChE結合。<br />\n<br />\n這些解毒劑雖然可以使患者康復起來，但患者的認知及肌肉功大有可能會有收到永久性的損害。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hf56hpy2SSQtx6ElJ%2BvIbMI%3D&h=962b012f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hf56hpy2SSQtx6ElJ%2BvIbMI%3D&h=d22f4056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科普資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。"},{"pid":"5ec63e1e91d6e5de3fe5fdae810ef2ba2b899663","tid":2186217,"uid":343385,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T20:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59fbdb5c7ac20d89578ebdec7c67421e435f445e","tid":2186217,"uid":46588,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T20:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長知識了"},{"pid":"606f4cb7528ece738d21c44379a0aa3743423b51","tid":2186217,"uid":34177,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T20:58:29.000Z","msg":"支持薯仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a85cfde06556837246a4f556cc6a03d747f0d5","tid":2186217,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T21:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/